Package utils

Class Dataset

java.lang.Object
utils.Dataset
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Chart, Curve, Particle, Particles, Surface
public abstract class Dataset extends Object implements Cloneable
Dataset is a abstract class that provides a unified interface for its subclasses. It serves the function of storing and manipulating coordinate objects.
Version:
0.2
Author:
Yuelong Li
